"TwentyFortyEight.instructions" = "# 2048\n\nCombine matching tiles on a 4×4 grid to reach the **2048** tile.\n\n## How to play\n\n- **Swipe** up, down, left, or right to slide every tile in that direction.\n- When two tiles with the **same number** collide, they merge into one tile with their **sum**.\n- After every move, a new **2** (or sometimes **4**) appears on a random empty cell.\n\n## Goal\n\nCreate a **2048** tile to win. After winning, you can keep going for a higher score.\n\n## Game over\n\nThe game ends when the board is full and no two adjacent tiles match.\n\n## Tips\n\n- Pick a corner and keep your largest tile parked there.\n- Build merges in a single direction so smaller tiles align underneath your big one.\n- On Easy, **undo** is available — use it to recover from mistakes.";
